msgstr "Installera 'less' om du vill rulla i denna lista"

#: APP-MANAGER:299
msgid ""
"💀 ERROR: Your version of sed does not support '-i' flag without extension, "
"we tried to workaround and failed"
msgstr ""
"💀 FEL: Din version av sed stöder inte '-i'-flaggan utan filändelse, vi "
"försökte med en lösning men misslyckades"

#: APP-MANAGER:300
msgid " Please install gsed"
msgstr " Installera gsed"

#: APP-MANAGER:315
msgid ""
"Before proceeding with any task, where do you want to install apps?\n"
"\n"
"SYNTAX: /FULLPATH/TO/DIRNAME\n"
"EXAMPLE: $HOME/My-apps\n"
"\n"
"NOTE: Any spaces in the path will be replaced for dashes\n"
"NOTE: If no input is given then \\\"~/Applications\\\" will be used as "
"default\n"
"\n"
"if you wish to later change the location, first remove all the programs and "
"then edit the \\\"$APPMANCONFIG/appman-config\\\" file."
msgstr ""
"Innan du fortsätter med någon uppgift, var vill du installera appar?\n"
"\n"
"SYNTAX: /HELSÖKVÄG/TILL/KATALOG\n"
"EXEMPEL: $HOME/Mina-appar\n"
"\n"
"OBSERVERA: Alla mellanslag i sökvägen kommer att ersättas med streck\n"
"OBSERVERA: Om ingen inmatning görs kommer \\\"~/Applications\\\" att "
"användas som standard\n"
"\n"
"om du senare vill ändra platsen, ta först bort alla program och redigera "
"sedan filen \\\"$APPMANCONFIG/appman-config\\\"."

#: APP-MANAGER:328
msgid ">>> Configure AppMan"
msgstr ">>> Konfigurera AppMan"

#: APP-MANAGER:328
msgid ">>> Thank you for choosing AppMan!"
msgstr ">>> Tack för att du väljer AppMan!"

